#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.40"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.40:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.40:0.2"
msgid "4. Kaḷārakhattiyavagga"
msgstr "4. Kaḷāra the Aristocrat"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.40:0.3"
msgid "40. Tatiyacetanāsutta"
msgstr "40. Intention"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.67"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.40:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn12.40:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Yañca, bhikkhave, ceteti yañca pakappeti yañca anuseti ārammaṇametaṃ hoti "
"viññāṇassa ṭhitiyā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, what you intend or plan, and what you have underlying "
"tendencies for become a support for the continuation of consciousness."

msgctxt "sn12.40:1.3"
msgid "Ārammaṇe sati patiṭṭhā viññāṇassa hoti."
msgstr "When this support exists, consciousness becomes established."

msgctxt "sn12.40:1.4"
msgid "Tasmiṃ patiṭṭhite viññāṇe virūḷhe nati hoti."
msgstr "When consciousness is established and grows, there is an inclination."

msgctxt "sn12.40:1.5"
msgid "Natiyā sati āgatigati hoti."
msgstr "When there is an inclination, there is coming and going."

msgctxt "sn12.40:1.6"
msgid "Āgatigatiyā sati cutūpapāto hoti."
msgstr "When there is coming and coming, there is passing away and reappearing."

msgctxt "sn12.40:1.7"
msgid ""
"Cutūpapāte sati āyatiṃ jāti jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā "
"sambhavanti."
msgstr ""
"When there is passing away and reappearing, future rebirth, old age, and "
"death come to be, as do sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress."

msgctxt "sn12.40:1.8"
msgid "Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.40:2.1"
msgid ""
"No ce, bhikkhave, ceteti no ce pakappeti atha ce anuseti, ārammaṇametaṃ hoti "
"viññāṇassa ṭhitiyā."
msgstr ""
"If you don’t intend or plan, but still have underlying tendencies, this "
"becomes a support for the continuation of consciousness."

msgctxt "sn12.40:2.2"
msgid "Ārammaṇe sati patiṭṭhā viññāṇassa hoti."
msgstr "When this support exists, consciousness becomes established."

msgctxt "sn12.40:2.3"
msgid "Tasmiṃ patiṭṭhite viññāṇe virūḷhe nati hoti."
msgstr "When consciousness is established and grows, there is an inclination."

msgctxt "sn12.40:2.4"
msgid "Natiyā sati āgatigati hoti."
msgstr "When there is an inclination, there is coming and going."

msgctxt "sn12.40:2.5"
msgid "Āgatigatiyā sati cutūpapāto hoti."
msgstr "When there is coming and coming, there is passing away and reappearing."

msgctxt "sn12.40:2.6"
msgid ""
"Cutūpapāte sati āyatiṃ jāti jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā "
"sambhavanti."
msgstr ""
"When there is passing away and reappearing, future rebirth, old age, and "
"death come to be, as do sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress."

msgctxt "sn12.40:2.7"
msgid "Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.40:3.1"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, no ceva ceteti no ca pakappeti no ca anuseti, "
"ārammaṇametaṃ na hoti viññāṇassa ṭhitiyā."
msgstr ""
"If you don’t intend or plan or have underlying tendencies, this doesn’t "
"become a support for the continuation of consciousness."

msgctxt "sn12.40:3.2"
msgid "Ārammaṇe asati patiṭṭhā viññāṇassa na hoti."
msgstr "With no support, consciousness is not established."

msgctxt "sn12.40:3.3"
msgid "Tadappatiṭṭhite viññāṇe avirūḷhe nati na hoti."
msgstr ""
"When consciousness is not established and doesn’t grow, there’s no "
"inclination."

msgctxt "sn12.40:3.4"
msgid "Natiyā asati āgatigati na hoti."
msgstr "When there’s no inclination, there’s no coming and going."

msgctxt "sn12.40:3.5"
msgid "Āgatigatiyā asati cutūpapāto na hoti."
msgstr ""
"When there’s no coming and coming, there’s no passing away and reappearing."

msgctxt "sn12.40:3.6"
msgid ""
"Cutūpapāte asati āyatiṃ jāti jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā "
"nirujjhanti."
msgstr ""
"When there’s no passing away and reappearing, future rebirth, old age, and "
"death cease, as do sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress."

msgctxt "sn12.40:3.7"
msgid "Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī”ti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.40:3.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.40:3.9"
msgid "Kaḷārakhattiyavaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.68"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.40:4.1"
msgid "Bhūtamidaṃ kaḷārañca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.40:4.2"
msgid "duve ca ñāṇavatthūni;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.40:4.3"
msgid "Avijjāpaccayā ca dve,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn12.40:4.4"
msgid "natumhā cetanā tayoti."
msgstr ""
